      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Cryo DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/35428890/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_2634128256174611251.png",
                "id": "talent76585",
                "key": "Icespike Shot",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Icespike Shot"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>. This character gains <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overwhelming Ice</span>.<br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\"><br>Overwhelming Ice</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character uses a Normal Attack:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span> to all opposing characters on standby . <br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/35428890/0124980d7537e933e9e0e819b78a0733_7640342703220052355.png",
                "id": "talent40895",
                "key": "Ice Ring Waltz",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Ice Ring Waltz"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>, deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span> to all opposing characters on standby, summons 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing Iceridge</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/35428890/77df8fb6101bdb6c35d501967b98f941_985731999445112862.png",
                "id": "talent20563",
                "key": "Plunging Ice Shards",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Plunging Ice Shards"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Passive Skill</span><br>(Passive) When the battle begins, this character gains <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Crystal Core</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Cryo Crystal Core</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character to which this is attached would be defeated:</span> Remove this effect, ensure the character <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">will not be defeated</span>, and heal them to 1 HP.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/31/35428890/c9fb58d0c17579d0eca97a167035bc53_4923983472403911245.png",
                "id": "talent91834",
                "key": "Cryo Crystal Core",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Cryo Crystal Core"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span> to the opposing <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Character Closest to Your Current Active Character</span>.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7801132524402748165.png",
                "id": "talent1508",
                "key": "Piercing Iceridge",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/35428890/9a3a650b50940ebaf9e842bccc80f213_2403922545959950438.png",
                "title": "Piercing Iceridge"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Cryo and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG+1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives Physical or Pyro DMG, in which case they will take +2 DMG)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/35428890/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_2127012702899561405.png",
                "id": "talent82586",
                "key": "Cryo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Cryo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Piercing DMG</span></strong><br>Piercing DMG cannot be increased by any bonuses, but cannot be defended against using Shields or DMG Immunity either.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span> of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span> remaining.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Character Closest to Your Current Active Character</span></strong><br>The opposing \"character closest to your current active character\" is the opposing character whose position is closest to that of your active character.<br>If multiple such characters exist, the one with the foremost position will be viewed as being \"closest.\"<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Immunity to Defeat</span></strong><br>Certain effects will grant characters an <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">immunity to being defeated</span> when their HP hits 0, and will heal them for a certain amount thereafter.<br>When this occurs, characters will not be regarded as having experienced a <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">defeat.</span> (Hence, their attached equipment and statuses will not be removed, and their Energy will remain uncleared.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_8199038528608193686.png",
                "id": "talent61080",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
